A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life of Khari Oramae Burns and recognizing March 8, 2025, as Infant
2 Emergency Awareness Day; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Khari Oramae Burns was born on November 30, 2023, in Atlanta, Georgia, at
4 Northside Hospital, bringing immeasurable joy to her family as a cherished daughter,
5 beloved sister, and radiant presence in the lives of all who knew her; and
6 WHEREAS, she was the only daughter of Erik Nickolas Burns Sr. and Brittany Nicole
7 Burns, whose unwavering love and care created a world filled with joy and laughter, as well
8 as the treasured little sister of Erik Nickolas Burns Jr., whose songs and presence brought her
9 endless comfort and delight; and
10 WHEREAS, her days were filled with love and simple joys, as she found great happiness in
11 watching her big brother play, splashing in warm baths, and sharing moments of music and
12 dance with her parents, always smiling and reaching out to be held; and
13 WHEREAS, with a sweet and gentle spirit, Khari Oramae Burns was known for her
14 comforting presence, bringing a sense of warmth and innocence to all who held her; and
